<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Improve the way attributs are retrive.
With the patch attributs are now retrive faster no need to get/filter the instances variable of the class.</p>

<p>The only thing is that whenever you setup an new attribut by just declaring it as an instance varibale you need to add the name in 
the variable {{$this-&gt;_attribsName}} for exemple:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
class MyElement extends Zend_Form_Element
{
  protected $href = 'foo.html';
  
  public function init()
  {
    $this-&gt;_attribsName = 'href';
  }
}
</code></pre>

<p>The method {{setAttribs($name, $value)}} is still working fine.</p>

<p>It is also probably better to patche element that adds some new attributs like: Zend_Form_Element_Image. 
See the patch for more details.</p>

